  <span id="freeText4422332710349733857" style="display:none">Three things: <br /><br />1. Zola's writing of abuse and domestic violence is breathtakingly modern; <br /><br />2. Poor old horse; and <br /><br />3. This novel contains a scene in which someone tears a dead man's dick off and parades it around on a stick. </span>
