<li class='cover' id='bookCover_59145'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59145.P_re_Goriot"><img alt="Père Goriot" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1389768126l/59145._SY160_.jpg" />
